# Core Agent Policy

Use `@AGENTS.md` as the canonical instruction set for this repository.

Apply these minimum rules in every task:

- Keep code artifacts in English.
- Do not hardcode translatable UI strings.
- Never introduce secrets or private credentials.
- Run relevant validation/tests after changes and report what ran.
